content:
CrossFit WOD:
Strength:
15min build up load for:
Power Snatch + Hang Squat Snatch + Overhead Squat (1+1+1)

Metcon:
For time:
21-15-9 reps of:
DB Front Squats (#22.5/15,x2)
Box Jump Overs
HSPU

Endurance:
In Pairs, for max distance in 38min:
Partner 1 - Row for distance
Partner 2 - 2 Rounds of:
12 Gorilla Rows (#16/12,x2)
9 Burpees to target
6 Ring Dips
*Switch roles when parter 2 finished his 2 rounds
